metadata.name: Intree Teddy #1
metadata.description:
This Special Teddy symbolizes the beginning of Intree Club. When owning this Intree Teddy, you show your support to privacy and a brighter future for social media.
You can find the Intree Club Founder collection here: https://opensea.io/collection/intreeclub

Visit https://www.intree.com/ to learn more about Intree as a company.
